thread.title: Oldest known cancer cases found in Egyptian mummies

title: Oldest known cancer cases found in Egyptian mummies
text:
Oldest known cancer cases found in Egyptian mummies Thursday, March 29, 2018 - 01:25 
The world's oldest known cases of breast cancer and multiple myeloma have been discovered in the remains of mummies in the pharaonic necropolis of Qubbet el-Hawa in the Egyptian city of Aswan. Jim Drury reports.
